{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>ShadowLess Light</u> is a visual novel with role-playing elements. You can create and customize your character attributes, skills and cybernetic implants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478790/extras/image.png?t=1740571689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You write the story by using <u>dice rolls</u> and making decisions, choosing between a stealthy or direct approach. Will you be charming or threatening? Do you want to use your wits or play the fool?\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478790/extras/Guide-7.gif?t=1740571689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s set in a dystopian <strong><u>Cyberpunk</u></strong> future, where justice is privatized by a megacorporation called ShadowLess Light. You are going to work as one of its agents, a ShadowLess: <u>judge, jury and executioner</u>, all rolled into one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478790/extras/Guide-6.gif?t=1740571689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features a system of notes and clues to keep track of all the information and gradually uncover the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478790/extras/Guide-2.gif?t=1740571689\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3478790?t=1740571689","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478790/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740571689","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478790/24e72b570db931d627d039ef64ccd01e2cd5645a/capsul